## ğŸ”„ API ENDPOINTS USED

| Action         | Method | Endpoint     | Payload           |
| -------------- | ------ | ------------ | ----------------- |
| Get Posts      | GET    | `/posts`     | â€”                 |
| Get Post by ID | GET    | `/posts/:id` | â€”                 |
| Add Post       | POST   | `/posts/add` | `{ title, body }` |
| Edit Post      | PUT    | `/posts/:id` | `{ title, body }` |
| Delete Post    | DELETE | `/posts/:id` | â€”                 |

